  m_Name: Oil-for-Peace Proposal
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::WarForOilEvent
  id: wfo_ofpc_01
  displayName: Oil-for-Peace Proposal
  description: The enemy is attempting to end the war by offering you a share of
    their oil revenues. The deal could bring immediate gains, but may fundamentally
    shift the balance of power and your long-term strategic position.
  devNote: 
  eventNote: "kar\u015F\u0131 taraf direkt olarak bize gelir ve gel sava\u015F\u0131
    bitirelim sana da g\xFCzel bir pay vereyim bizi sal der\n\nd\xFCzg\xFCnce reddeder
    sava\u015Fa devam edersin war supportunu artt\u0131r\u0131r az\u0131c\u0131k
    da bi siyasi n\xFCfuz kazan\u0131r yoluna devam edersin\n\nkabul edersin ve anla\u015Fmadan
    pay\u0131n\u0131 al\u0131rs\u0131n ancak siyasi n\xFCfuzun dibi boylar \u015F\xFCphen
    u\xE7ar\n\nveya kabul etmeyip hem de teklifi if\u015Fa edersin b\xF6ylece siyasi
    n\xFCfuzun iyi artar itibar\u0131n biraz artar ancak sava\u015F s\xFCresince
    daha kendi iste\u011Finle ate\u015Fkes yapamazs\u0131n(di\u011Fer eventlerin
    choice lar\u0131 veya sonucu ate\u015Fkese ba\u011Flanabilir ama hala)\n"
